<P>A TRUE and FAITHFUL ACCOUNT OF THE GREATEST WONDER Produced by NATURE the&s;e 3000 Years, In the PERSON of Mr. JEHAN-PAUL-ERNEST CHRISTIAN LODOVICK MANPFERDT; The SURPRIZING CENTAUR, Who will be exhibited to the Publick, on the fir&s;t of next Month, at the Sign of the <HI>Golden Gro&s;s</HI> at <HI>Charing-Cro&s;s.</HI></P>
